with codecs.open('testdata/models/routing_public_time_table.json', mode='r',
    encoding='utf-8') as f:
    expectedResponse = f.read()
responses.add(responses.GET,
    'https://route.ls.hereapi.com/routing/7.2/calculateroute.json',
    expectedResponse, status=200)
response = self._api.public_transport_timetable([11.0, 12.0], [15.0, 16.0],
    True)
expected_short_route = (
    '330 - Archer/Harlem (Terminal); 309 - Elmhurst Metra Station')
self.assertEqual(response.route_short, expected_short_route)
responses.activate
